HEADWORD: Countrywoman
<hw>Coun"try*wom`an</hw> <pr>(-w??m`<it>a</it>n)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>;
<plu><it>pl.</it> <plw>Countrywomen</plw> <pr>(-w<?/m`<?/n)</pr>.</plu>
